title: Haven't been put in a ranked division? (i.e. Bronze V)

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body:
Hey all,

Here's a link to my (atrocious) match history. I've played more than 10 ranked games but haven't been ranked yet? If anyone knows what i'm meant to do that'd be great... Thanks.

replies.body: That's super odd. Are you sure that all 10 ranked games were all in the same queue (ie. Flex Queue or Solo/Duo Queue, but not both)?
Pretty confident they were all solo queue- is there a way to check?
I've been told that you've played 9 Solo Queue matches this season, along with 2 Flex Queue matches.
